# Build test
npm run build

# Lighthouse test
npx lighthouse http://localhost:3000
```

### Git Workflow
```bash
# Create feature branch
git checkout -b feature/[nome]

# Commit changes
git add .
git commit -m "type: description"

# Push to origin
git push origin feature/[nome]

# Merge to main
git checkout main
git merge feature/[nome]
git push origin main
```

### Production Deploy
```bash
# Build production
npm run build

# Deploy to Vercel
vercel --prod

# Check deployment
vercel ls
```

